    "body": "This PR adds a user-friendly check for: https://github.com/tile-ai/tilelang/issues/1335\n\n<!-- This is an auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->\n\n## Summary by CodeRabbit\n\n* **Improvements**\n  * Enhanced error messages with more descriptive diagnostics for invalid symbolic shape configurations.\n  * Strengthened pre-lowering semantic validation to detect invalid loop-buffer access patterns at an earlier compilation stage.\n  * Standardized error message formatting across validation checks for improved consistency.\n\n* **Tests**\n  * Added comprehensive test suite covering various loop validation scenarios.\n\n<sub>✏️ Tip: You can customize this high-level summary in your review settings.</sub>\n\n<!-- end of auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->",
